title: The Concept of Neurodiversity In Transport
subtitle: Initial concept, intial website
tags: [initial]
---

This is the initial first news article. Setting up a website as a framework of how Neurodiversity In Transport could operate. The rough sections act as place holders for which content could be added and act as a starting point.

The aims, trustees and sponsors need much more thought. The Employers toolkit with sections of Work Experience, Recruiting, On-boarding and then when a person is employed maximising-potential - feels like a good starting point. Fix the employers, not the employee. 
